Ketika saya bercakap,

546
00:24:12,679 --> 00:24:13,959
terus jadi lain pula.

547
00:24:18,320 --> 00:24:20,479
Mengapa jadi begitu?

548
00:24:26,239 --> 00:24:28,199
Fikiran saya amat negatif.

549
00:24:31,120 --> 00:24:32,800
Negatif sahaja.

550
00:24:39,520 --> 00:24:40,439
Xin,

551
00:24:41,320 --> 00:24:42,919
