552
00:24:44,040 --> 00:24:45,040
Awak juga jangan terlalu memikirkannya.

553
00:24:46,280 --> 00:24:47,320
Terutamanya,

554
00:24:48,679 --> 00:24:50,840
kakak rasa keadaan awak sekarang

555
00:24:51,919 --> 00:24:53,439
