00:25:30,280 --> 00:25:31,320
Sudikah awak?

570
00:25:38,120 --> 00:25:38,639
Jangan risau.

571
00:25:40,479 --> 00:25:41,479
Biar kakak peluk sebentar.

572
00:25:48,919 --> 00:25:49,679
Tiada mengapa.

