00:27:38,840 --> 00:27:40,320
Namun, kedua-dua perasaan ini

592
00:27:41,959 --> 00:27:43,120
asyik berlawan

593
00:27:43,919 --> 00:27:45,320
dalam hatinya.

594
00:27:47,399 --> 00:27:48,360
[Maka,]

595
00:27:49,080 --> 00:27:50,560
dia rasa hilang keyakinan

596
00:27:51,520 --> 00:27:52,800
terhadap semua orang di sisinya,

