00:27:54,239 --> 00:27:55,439
malah termasuk diri sendiri.

598
00:27:56,840 --> 00:27:57,800
[Tambahan pula,

599
00:27:58,959 --> 00:28:00,959
perhatian orang ramai terhadap ibu
