00:29:46,520 --> 00:29:48,679
[Saya pergi berjalan-jalan di luar bandar.]

631
00:29:48,879 --> 00:29:50,399
Saya menikmati perasaan

632
00:29:50,399 --> 00:29:51,639
di bawah cahaya matahari

633
00:29:51,639 --> 00:29:52,679
dan alam sekitar.

634
00:29:53,120 --> 00:29:54,360
Saya rasa amat selesa.

