00:30:01,719 --> 00:30:03,760
saya rasa mudah untuk
memahami perasaan orang lain.

640
00:30:04,840 --> 00:30:05,840
Bagus!

641
00:30:42,159 --> 00:30:43,679
Mak, saya sudah balik.

642
00:30:47,639 --> 00:30:48,560
Kak Yingzi.

643
00:31:00,719 --> 00:31:01,719
[Haowen.]

644
00:31:57,679 --> 00:31:59,040
Macam mana? Sudahkah diluluskan?

645
00:32:01,600 --> 00:32:02,560
Sudahkah diluluskan atau tidak?

646
00:32:02,560 --> 00:32:03,239
Awak tengoklah sendiri.

647
00:32:06,639 --> 00:32:07,600
Sudah lulus!

