pelaburan dalam Lanhai.

650
00:32:10,399 --> 00:32:11,399
Tahniah, Encik Yu.

651
00:32:12,159 --> 00:32:13,320
Terima kasih.

652
00:32:13,639 --> 00:32:15,199
Saya harus berterima kasih kepada awak.

653
00:32:15,520 --> 00:32:17,199
Sebabnya bantuan awak,

654
00:32:17,399 --> 00:32:18,239
