695
00:33:31,040 --> 00:33:31,919
Buku nota.

696
00:33:35,159 --> 00:33:36,040
Pulangkan kepadanya.

697
00:33:45,560 --> 00:33:46,239
Sayang.

698
00:33:46,479 --> 00:33:47,280
Sudah balik.

