Yunjie,

705
00:33:59,280 --> 00:34:00,360
mari tengok makanan apa

706
00:34:00,360 --> 00:34:01,840
yang mak awak beli?

707
00:34:02,879 --> 00:34:04,080
Mari, tengok.

708
00:34:06,639 --> 00:34:07,679
Apakah tujuan mak?

709
00:34:10,520 --> 00:34:11,879
Walaupun nampak

