728
00:34:42,239 --> 00:34:43,239
keluarga Zhu Kexin

729
00:34:43,239 --> 00:34:44,520
begitu susah.

730
00:34:46,080 --> 00:34:47,839
Betul. Jadi, saya rasa,

731
00:34:47,839 --> 00:34:48,799
tak boleh lagi saya

732
00:34:48,799 --> 00:34:49,679
